{"title":"黄河砥柱","authors":["董耀章"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":11,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河砥柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董耀章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮起潮落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪平浪啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三门峡仰天长歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河水一泻滔滔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层叠叠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叠叠层层"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月挤压在岩层深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说着晨钟暮鼓代代朝朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大禹奔波的足迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长出了一篇篇神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈山夺路的板斧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蕴藉了一曲曲民谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大坝巍巍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锁住了黄水胎生的野性"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清波粼粼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿了华夏大地漫漫诗涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望神门——早已隐了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望鬼门——早已藏了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望人门——感叹三声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早沉入水底暗暗自嘲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风明月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沧桑古道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史捧镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照出了人间的悲欢离合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔帆点点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语涌潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日溶金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托现出黄河儿女的一代风骚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中流砥柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天塑神雕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开天辟地一身铁骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古往今来辉耀碧霄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只只船儿脱险了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一排排恶浪败阵了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中流砥柱啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一尊不朽丰碑耸立黄河水道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中流砥柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个晶晶亮亮的水洗词汇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的存在是为了甩开苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的理想是为了超越崇高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你腔里有一团浩然正气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你大脑中有一个闪光信条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为抒写人间真情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为描绘大地画稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你守护中华文化的摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你展示着古老民族的景潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的风景线在这里拉开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幕一幕从远古文明到辉煌今朝……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}